In the review process, that is why we ask to submit related packages under the same issue.  They will be installed in the same location and available for testing before being added to the official Bioconductor repositories (once officially added available through BiocManager::install)

You can use the github link for testing on your machine, But put the data package as an appropriate Import/Suggests (or Depends) in the DESCRIPTION/NAMESPACE before submitting to Bioconductor issue review.

